                Started as an IBM guided notebook covering basic price and revenue charts for two stocks.
                Rebuilt into a fully automated, config-driven pipeline: extract historical prices via
                yfinance and quarterly revenue via web scraping, validate and structure the data, compute
                five financial metrics, and generate nine interactive Plotly visualizations across five
                tickers and an S&P 500 benchmark.
              </p>
